To install this system, Use Debian (jessie), and run this script

scripts/fix-deps

To clean an existing build tree 

scripts/clean-all

To build all packages

make packages

To build a specific package

make <package name>-ipk

To rebuilt the package repository

make index

Package repository is created in the packages folder after a make packages
or make index has been run, simply copy the repository to its hosting
space to deploy.

For detailed instructions on how to build packages using this build system, see:

  http://www.nslu2-linux.org/wiki/Optware/AddAPackageToOptware

